"seem to know, and neither do we. Still, it's as good a name as any, and it "
"seems to have stuck.\n"
"\n"
"That's all I have for you right now, Commander. I'll contact you again as "
"soon as something new develops.\n"
"\n"
"Sincerely,\n"
"\n"
"Dr. Connor"
